  "texts": [
    "The ReRAM to systolic array MM can be expressed as follows: 𝑀𝑀 𝑅𝑒𝑅𝐴𝑀 𝑀𝑀 𝑆𝑦𝑠𝑡𝑜𝑙𝑖𝑐 ∝ 𝑂 ( 12 × 𝑑 𝑚𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑙 2. 𝑛 𝑑 𝑚𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑙.",
    "𝑛 2 + 2𝑘 × 𝑑 𝑚𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑙.",
    "𝑟. 𝑛 + 3 × 𝑑 𝑚𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑙.",
    "𝑛) Here, 𝑑 𝑚𝑜𝑑𝑒𝑙, 𝑛, 𝑟 and 𝑘 represent the model dimension, input sequence length, rank for the LoRA matrices, and the number of LoRA matrices in each layer, respectively.",
    "For the scenario considered here, k = 2."
  ],
